Recommended Libraries:

 Below are some commonly used libraries we use at WillowTree Apps.

 * {{{http://square.github.io/dagger/} Dagger}} - Dependency Injection.

 * {{{http://square.github.io/okhttp/} OkHttp}} - Http Client.

 * {{{http://jakewharton.github.io/butterknife/} Butterknife}} - View Injection.

 * {{{http://square.github.io/picasso/} Picasso}} - Image Loading.

 * {{{http://square.github.io/otto/} Otto}} - Event Bus.

 * {{{https://github.com/Netflix/RxJava/tree/master/rxjava-contrib/rxjava-android} RxJava}}



